snippet.title: TIME TRAVEL SHANTY - A Time-Travel Puzzle Game (GMTK Game Jam 2020)
snippet.description:
Showcase of the game prototype I made for GMTK GameJam 2020: Out of Control.
A cursed gem causes out of control time travel! Collect treasure, face undead skeletons and explore two worlds in one. 

Play and rate the game: https://itch.io/jam/gmtk-2020/rate/700907
Twitter: https://twitter.com/gypynkt
Music by Tunglith: https://tunglith.com
